data.description: Welcome to 30 Andrew Ct, a captivating home nestled in the serene Logan Township with low taxes all on a quiet cul-de-sac. This property is a hidden gem, boasting an array of features that blend comfort with convenience, all set in a friendly neighborhood.  Key Features:  Low Taxes: Enjoy the financial benefits of low taxes, making this an economical choice for savvy buyers. Fully Fenced Rear Yard: Safety and privacy are paramount with a spacious, fully fenced rear yard, perfect for outdoor activities and secure for pets. Three Comfortable Bedrooms: Each bedroom is designed to offer a tranquil retreat, providing ample space for rest and relaxation. One and a Half Bathrooms: The 1.5 baths were recently renovated and offer a relaxing getaway experience.   Huge Eat-in Kitchen: A culinary haven, the large eat-in kitchen is perfect for family meals and entertaining, featuring modern appliances and plenty of storage. One-Car Attached Garage: The convenience of an attached garage offers secure parking and additional storage space. This property is an ideal blend of comfort and convenience, situated in a peaceful community with easy access to local amenities. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, looking to downsize, or looking to move up, 30 Andrew Ct offers a perfect balance of tranquility and practicality.  Don’t miss out on this opportunity to make 30 Andrew Ct your new home! Contact us for a viewing and take the first step towards your dream home.  Make sure to check out the 3D virtual tour.
